In [4]:
Year=[]
car_name=[]
Add = []
Kmt=[]
fuel=[]
Trans=[]
Price = []
kmt1 =[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= r"\b\d{4}\b"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        Year.append(regex[0])
    else:
        Year.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= " \w+"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        car_name.append(regex)
    else:
        car_name.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    add = i.find('span',class_="_3DYbK")
    if add:
        Add.append(add.text)
    else:
        Add.append(np.nan)
Kmt=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"\d{1,3},\d{2,3}|[,]\d{1,3}"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        Kmt.append(regex)
    else:
        Kmt.append(np.nan)

fuel=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"Petrol|Diesel"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        fuel.append(regex)
    else:
        fuel.append(np.nan)



for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    trans = i.find('ul',class_='_1hOnS').text
    pattern= r"Manual|Automatic"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,trans)
    if regex:
        Trans.append(regex)
    else:
        Trans.append(np.nan)


for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    price= i.find('div',class_="_18ToE").text
    yoo = price.split("₹")[1].replace(",","")
    Price.append(yoo)

kmt1 = []
dicto["Kmt run"]
for i in dicto["Kmt run"]:
    a = str(i).replace('[','')
    b = a.replace(' ','')
    c = b.replace(',','')
    d = c.replace(']','')
    e = d.replace("''",'')
    kmt1.append(int(e.strip("'")))

Year=[]
car_name=[]
Add = []
Kmt=[]
fuel=[]
Trans=[]
Price = []
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= r"\b\d{4}\b"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        Year.append(regex[0])
    else:
        Year.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= " \w+"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        car_name.append(regex)
    else:
        car_name.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    add = i.find('span',class_="_3DYbK")
    if add:
        Add.append(add.text)
    else:
        Add.append(np.nan)
Kmt=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"\d{1,3},\d{2,3}|[,]\d{1,3}"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        Kmt.append(regex)
    else:
        Kmt.append(np.nan)

fuel=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"Petrol|Diesel"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        fuel.append(regex)
    else:
        fuel.append(np.nan)



for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    trans = i.find('ul',class_='_1hOnS').text
    pattern= r"Manual|Automatic"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,trans)
    if regex:
        Trans.append(regex)
    else:
        Trans.append(np.nan)


for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    price= i.find('div',class_="_18ToE").text
    yoo = price.split("₹")[1].replace(",","")
    Price.append(yoo)

Year=[]
car_name=[]
Add = []
Kmt=[]
fuel=[]
Trans=[]
Price = []
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= r"\b\d{4}\b"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        Year.append(regex[0])
    else:
        Year.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= " \w+"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        car_name.append(regex)
    else:
        car_name.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    add = i.find('span',class_="_3DYbK")
    if add:
        Add.append(add.text)
    else:
        Add.append(np.nan)
Kmt=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"\d{1,3},\d{2,3}|[,]\d{1,3}"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        Kmt.append(regex)
    else:
        Kmt.append(np.nan)

fuel=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"Petrol|Diesel"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        fuel.append(regex)
    else:
        fuel.append(np.nan)



for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    trans = i.find('ul',class_='_1hOnS').text
    pattern= r"Manual|Automatic"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,trans)
    if regex:
        Trans.append(regex)
    else:
        Trans.append(np.nan)



for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    price= i.find('div',class_="_18ToE").text
    yoo = price.split("₹")[1].replace(",","")
    Price.append(yoo)

Year=[]
car_name=[]
Add = []
Kmt=[]
fuel=[]
Trans=[]
Price = []
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= r"\b\d{4}\b"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        Year.append(regex[0])
    else:
        Year.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= " \w+"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        car_name.append(regex)
    else:
        car_name.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    add = i.find('span',class_="_3DYbK")
    if add:
        Add.append(add.text)
    else:
        Add.append(np.nan)
Kmt=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"\d{1,3},\d{2,3}|[,]\d{1,3}"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        Kmt.append(regex)
    else:
        Kmt.append(np.nan)

fuel=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"Petrol|Diesel"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        fuel.append(regex)
    else:
        fuel.append(np.nan)



for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    trans = i.find('ul',class_='_1hOnS').text
    pattern= r"Manual|Automatic"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,trans)
    if regex:
        Trans.append(regex)
    else:
        Trans.append(np.nan)


for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    price= i.find('div',class_="_18ToE").text
    yoo = price.split("₹")[1].replace(",","")
    Price.append(yoo)

Year=[]
car_name=[]
Add = []
Kmt=[]
fuel=[]
Trans=[]
Price = []
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= r"\b\d{4}\b"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        Year.append(regex[0])
    else:
        Year.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= " \w+"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        car_name.append(regex)
    else:
        car_name.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    add = i.find('span',class_="_3DYbK")
    if add:
        Add.append(add.text)
    else:
        Add.append(np.nan)
Kmt=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"\d{1,3},\d{2,3}|[,]\d{1,3}"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        Kmt.append(regex)
    else:
        Kmt.append(np.nan)

fuel=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"Petrol|Diesel"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        fuel.append(regex)
    else:
        fuel.append(np.nan)



for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    trans = i.find('ul',class_='_1hOnS').text
    pattern= r"Manual|Automatic"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,trans)
    if regex:
        Trans.append(regex)
    else:
        Trans.append(np.nan)


for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    price= i.find('div',class_="_18ToE").text
    yoo = price.split("₹")[1].replace(",","")
    Price.append(yoo)

Year=[]
car_name=[]
Add = []
Kmt=[]
fuel=[]
Trans=[]
Price = []
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= r"\b\d{4}\b"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        Year.append(regex[0])
    else:
        Year.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= " \w+"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        car_name.append(regex)
    else:
        car_name.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    add = i.find('span',class_="_3DYbK")
    if add:
        Add.append(add.text)
    else:
        Add.append(np.nan)
Kmt=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"\d{1,3},\d{2,3}|[,]\d{1,3}"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        Kmt.append(regex)
    else:
        Kmt.append(np.nan)

fuel=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"Petrol|Diesel"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        fuel.append(regex)
    else:
        fuel.append(np.nan)



for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    trans = i.find('ul',class_='_1hOnS').text
    pattern= r"Manual|Automatic"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,trans)
    if regex:
        Trans.append(regex)
    else:
        Trans.append(np.nan)


for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    price= i.find('div',class_="_18ToE").text
    yoo = price.split("₹")[1].replace(",","")
    Price.append(yoo)

Year=[]
car_name=[]
Add = []
Kmt=[]
fuel=[]
Trans=[]
Price = []
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= r"\b\d{4}\b"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        Year.append(regex[0])
    else:
        Year.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= " \w+"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        car_name.append(regex)
    else:
        car_name.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    add = i.find('span',class_="_3DYbK")
    if add:
        Add.append(add.text)
    else:
        Add.append(np.nan)
Kmt=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"\d{1,3},\d{2,3}|[,]\d{1,3}"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        Kmt.append(regex)
    else:
        Kmt.append(np.nan)

fuel=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"Petrol|Diesel"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        fuel.append(regex)
    else:
        fuel.append(np.nan)



for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    trans = i.find('ul',class_='_1hOnS').text
    pattern= r"Manual|Automatic"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,trans)
    if regex:
        Trans.append(regex)
    else:
        Trans.append(np.nan)


for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    price= i.find('div',class_="_18ToE").text
    yoo = price.split("₹")[1].replace(",","")
    Price.append(yoo)

Year=[]
car_name=[]
Add = []
Kmt=[]
fuel=[]
Trans=[]
Price = []
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= r"\b\d{4}\b"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        Year.append(regex[0])
    else:
        Year.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= " \w+"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        car_name.append(regex)
    else:
        car_name.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    add = i.find('span',class_="_3DYbK")
    if add:
        Add.append(add.text)
    else:
        Add.append(np.nan)
Kmt=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"\d{1,3},\d{2,3}|[,]\d{1,3}"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        Kmt.append(regex)
    else:
        Kmt.append(np.nan)

fuel=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"Petrol|Diesel"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        fuel.append(regex)
    else:
        fuel.append(np.nan)



for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    trans = i.find('ul',class_='_1hOnS').text
    pattern= r"Manual|Automatic"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,trans)
    if regex:
        Trans.append(regex)
    else:
        Trans.append(np.nan)


for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    price= i.find('div',class_="_18ToE").text
    yoo = price.split("₹")[1].replace(",","")
    Price.append(yoo)

Year=[]
car_name=[]
Add = []
Kmt=[]
fuel=[]
Trans=[]
Price = []
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= r"\b\d{4}\b"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        Year.append(regex[0])
    else:
        Year.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= " \w+"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        car_name.append(regex)
    else:
        car_name.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    add = i.find('span',class_="_3DYbK")
    if add:
        Add.append(add.text)
    else:
        Add.append(np.nan)
Kmt=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"\d{1,3},\d{2,3}|[,]\d{1,3}"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        Kmt.append(regex)
    else:
        Kmt.append(np.nan)

fuel=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"Petrol|Diesel"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        fuel.append(regex)
    else:
        fuel.append(np.nan)



for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    trans = i.find('ul',class_='_1hOnS').text
    pattern= r"Manual|Automatic"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,trans)
    if regex:
        Trans.append(regex)
    else:
        Trans.append(np.nan)


for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    price= i.find('div',class_="_18ToE").text
    yoo = price.split("₹")[1].replace(",","")
    Price.append(yoo)

Year=[]
car_name=[]
Add = []
Kmt=[]
fuel=[]
Trans=[]
Price = []
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= r"\b\d{4}\b"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        Year.append(regex[0])
    else:
        Year.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= " \w+"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        car_name.append(regex)
    else:
        car_name.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    add = i.find('span',class_="_3DYbK")
    if add:
        Add.append(add.text)
    else:
        Add.append(np.nan)
Kmt=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"\d{1,3},\d{2,3}|[,]\d{1,3}"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        Kmt.append(regex)
    else:
        Kmt.append(np.nan)

fuel=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"Petrol|Diesel"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        fuel.append(regex)
    else:
        fuel.append(np.nan)



for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    trans = i.find('ul',class_='_1hOnS').text
    pattern= r"Manual|Automatic"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,trans)
    if regex:
        Trans.append(regex)
    else:
        Trans.append(np.nan)


for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    price= i.find('div',class_="_18ToE").text
    yoo = price.split("₹")[1].replace(",","")
    Price.append(yoo)

Year=[]
car_name=[]
Add = []
Kmt=[]
fuel=[]
Trans=[]
Price = []
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= r"\b\d{4}\b"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        Year.append(regex[0])
    else:
        Year.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= " \w+"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        car_name.append(regex)
    else:
        car_name.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    add = i.find('span',class_="_3DYbK")
    if add:
        Add.append(add.text)
    else:
        Add.append(np.nan)
Kmt=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"\d{1,3},\d{2,3}|[,]\d{1,3}"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        Kmt.append(regex)
    else:
        Kmt.append(np.nan)

fuel=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"Petrol|Diesel"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        fuel.append(regex)
    else:
        fuel.append(np.nan)



for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    trans = i.find('ul',class_='_1hOnS').text
    pattern= r"Manual|Automatic"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,trans)
    if regex:
        Trans.append(regex)
    else:
        Trans.append(np.nan)

    price= i.find('div',class_="_18ToE").text
    yoo = price.split("₹")[1].replace(",","")
    Price.append(yoo)

Year=[]
car_name=[]
Add = []
Kmt=[]
fuel=[]
Trans=[]
Price = []
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= r"\b\d{4}\b"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        Year.append(regex[0])
    else:
        Year.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= " \w+"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        car_name.append(regex)
    else:
        car_name.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    add = i.find('span',class_="_3DYbK")
    if add:
        Add.append(add.text)
    else:
        Add.append(np.nan)
Kmt=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"\d{1,3},\d{2,3}|[,]\d{1,3}"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        Kmt.append(regex)
    else:
        Kmt.append(np.nan)

fuel=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"Petrol|Diesel"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        fuel.append(regex)
    else:
        fuel.append(np.nan)



for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    trans = i.find('ul',class_='_1hOnS').text
    pattern= r"Manual|Automatic"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,trans)
    if regex:
        Trans.append(regex)
    else:
        Trans.append(np.nan)


for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    price= i.find('div',class_="_18ToE").text
    yoo = price.split("₹")[1].replace(",","")
    Price.append(yoo)
    
    
print(Year)

Year=[]
car_name=[]
Add = []
Kmt=[]
fuel=[]
Trans=[]
Price = []
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= r"\b\d{4}\b"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        Year.append(regex[0])
    else:
        Year.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= " \w+"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        car_name.append(regex)
    else:
        car_name.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    add = i.find('span',class_="_3DYbK")
    if add:
        Add.append(add.text)
    else:
        Add.append(np.nan)
Kmt=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"\d{1,3},\d{2,3}|[,]\d{1,3}"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        Kmt.append(regex)
    else:
        Kmt.append(np.nan)

fuel=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"Petrol|Diesel"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        fuel.append(regex)
    else:
        fuel.append(np.nan)



for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    trans = i.find('ul',class_='_1hOnS').text
    pattern= r"Manual|Automatic"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,trans)
    if regex:
        Trans.append(regex)
    else:
        Trans.append(np.nan)


for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    price= i.find('div',class_="_18ToE").text
    yoo = price.split("₹")[1].replace(",","")
    Price.append(yoo)

Year=[]
car_name=[]
Add = []
Kmt=[]
fuel=[]
Trans=[]
Price = []
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= r"\b\d{4}\b"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        Year.append(regex[0])
    else:
        Year.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= " \w+"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        car_name.append(regex)
    else:
        car_name.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    add = i.find('span',class_="_3DYbK")
    if add:
        Add.append(add.text)
    else:
        Add.append(np.nan)
Kmt=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"\d{1,3},\d{2,3}|[,]\d{1,3}"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        Kmt.append(regex)
    else:
        Kmt.append(np.nan)

fuel=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"Petrol|Diesel"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        fuel.append(regex)
    else:
        fuel.append(np.nan)



for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    trans = i.find('ul',class_='_1hOnS').text
    pattern= r"Manual|Automatic"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,trans)
    if regex:
        Trans.append(regex)
    else:
        Trans.append(np.nan)


for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    price= i.find('div',class_="_18ToE").text
    yoo = price.split("₹")[1].replace(",","")
    Price.append(yoo)

Year=[]
car_name=[]
Add = []
Kmt=[]
fuel=[]
Trans=[]
Price = []
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= r"\b\d{4}\b"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        Year.append(regex[0])
    else:
        Year.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= " \w+"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        car_name.append(regex)
    else:
        car_name.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    add = i.find('span',class_="_3DYbK")
    if add:
        Add.append(add.text)
    else:
        Add.append(np.nan)
Kmt=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"\d{1,3},\d{2,3}|[,]\d{1,3}"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        Kmt.append(regex)
    else:
        Kmt.append(np.nan)

fuel=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"Petrol|Diesel"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        fuel.append(regex)
    else:
        fuel.append(np.nan)



for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    trans = i.find('ul',class_='_1hOnS').text
    pattern= r"Manual|Automatic"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,trans)
    if regex:
        Trans.append(regex)
    else:
        Trans.append(np.nan)


for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    price= i.find('div',class_="_18ToE").text
    yoo = price.split("₹")[1].replace(",","")
    Price.append(yoo)

Year=[]
car_name=[]
Add = []
Kmt=[]
fuel=[]
Trans=[]
Price = []
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= r"\b\d{4}\b"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        Year.append(regex[0])
    else:
        Year.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= " \w+"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        car_name.append(regex)
    else:
        car_name.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    add = i.find('span',class_="_3DYbK")
    if add:
        Add.append(add.text)
    else:
        Add.append(np.nan)
Kmt=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"\d{1,3},\d{2,3}|[,]\d{1,3}"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        Kmt.append(regex)
    else:
        Kmt.append(np.nan)

fuel=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"Petrol|Diesel"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        fuel.append(regex)
    else:
        fuel.append(np.nan)



for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    trans = i.find('ul',class_='_1hOnS').text
    pattern= r"Manual|Automatic"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,trans)
    if regex:
        Trans.append(regex)
    else:
        Trans.append(np.nan)


for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    price= i.find('div',class_="_18ToE").text
    yoo = price.split("₹")[1].replace(",","")
    Price.append(yoo)

Year=[]
car_name=[]
Add = []
Kmt=[]
fuel=[]
Trans=[]
Price = []
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= r"\b\d{4}\b"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        Year.append(regex[0])
    else:
        Year.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= " \w+"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        car_name.append(regex)
    else:
        car_name.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    add = i.find('span',class_="_3DYbK")
    if add:
        Add.append(add.text)
    else:
        Add.append(np.nan)
Kmt=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"\d{1,3},\d{2,3}|[,]\d{1,3}"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        Kmt.append(regex)
    else:
        Kmt.append(np.nan)

fuel=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"Petrol|Diesel"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        fuel.append(regex)
    else:
        fuel.append(np.nan)



for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    trans = i.find('ul',class_='_1hOnS').text
    pattern= r"Manual|Automatic"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,trans)
    if regex:
        Trans.append(regex)
    else:
        Trans.append(np.nan)


for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    price= i.find('div',class_="_18ToE").text
    yoo = price.split("₹")[1].replace(",","")
    Price.append(yoo)
    
    
print(Year)

Year=[]
car_name=[]
Add = []
Kmt=[]
fuel=[]
Trans=[]
Price = []
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= r"\b\d{4}\b"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        Year.append(regex[0])
    else:
        Year.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= " \w+"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        car_name.append(regex)
    else:
        car_name.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    add = i.find('span',class_="_3DYbK")
    if add:
        Add.append(add.text)
    else:
        Add.append(np.nan)
Kmt=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"\d{1,3},\d{2,3}|[,]\d{1,3}"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        Kmt.append(regex)
    else:
        Kmt.append(np.nan)

fuel=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"Petrol|Diesel"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        fuel.append(regex)
    else:
        fuel.append(np.nan)



for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    trans = i.find('ul',class_='_1hOnS').text
    pattern= r"Manual|Automatic"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,trans)
    if regex:
        Trans.append(regex)
    else:
        Trans.append(np.nan)


for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    price= i.find('div',class_="_18ToE").text
    yoo = price.split("₹")[1].replace(",","")
    Price.append(yoo)

Year=[]
car_name=[]
Add = []

fuel=[]

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= r"\b\d{4}\b"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        Year.append(regex[0])
    else:
        Year.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= " \w+"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        car_name.append(regex)
    else:
        car_name.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    add = i.find('span',class_="_3DYbK")
    if add:
        Add.append(add.text)
    else:
        Add.append(np.nan)
Kmt=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"\d{1,3},\d{2,3}|[,]\d{1,3}"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        Kmt.append(regex)
    else:
        Kmt.append(np.nan)

fuel=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"Petrol|Diesel"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        fuel.append(regex)
    else:
        fuel.append(np.nan)



for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    trans = i.find('ul',class_='_1hOnS').text
    pattern= r"Manual|Automatic"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,trans)
    if regex:
        Trans.append(regex)
    else:
        Trans.append(np.nan)


for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    price= i.find('div',class_="_18ToE").text
    yoo = price.split("₹")[1].replace(",","")
    Price.append(yoo)

Year=[]
car_name=[]
Add = []
Kmt=[]
fuel=[]
Trans=[]
Price = []
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= r"\b\d{4}\b"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        Year.append(regex[0])
    else:
        Year.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= " \w+"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        car_name.append(regex)
    else:
        car_name.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    add = i.find('span',class_="_3DYbK")
    if add:
        Add.append(add.text)
    else:
        Add.append(np.nan)
Kmt=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"\d{1,3},\d{2,3}|[,]\d{1,3}"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        Kmt.append(regex)
    else:
        Kmt.append(np.nan)

fuel=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"Petrol|Diesel"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        fuel.append(regex)
    else:
        fuel.append(np.nan)



for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    trans = i.find('ul',class_='_1hOnS').text
    pattern= r"Manual|Automatic"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,trans)
    if regex:
        Trans.append(regex)
    else:
        Trans.append(np.nan)


for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    price= i.find('div',class_="_18ToE").text
    yoo = price.split("₹")[1].replace(",","")
    Price.append(yoo)

Year=[]
car_name=[]
Add = []
Kmt=[]
fuel=[]
Trans=[]
Price = []
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= r"\b\d{4}\b"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        Year.append(regex[0])
    else:
        Year.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= " \w+"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        car_name.append(regex)
    else:
        car_name.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    add = i.find('span',class_="_3DYbK")
    if add:
        Add.append(add.text)
    else:
        Add.append(np.nan)
Kmt=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"\d{1,3},\d{2,3}|[,]\d{1,3}"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        Kmt.append(regex)
    else:
        Kmt.append(np.nan)

fuel=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"Petrol|Diesel"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        fuel.append(regex)
    else:
        fuel.append(np.nan)



for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    trans = i.find('ul',class_='_1hOnS').text
    pattern= r"Manual|Automatic"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,trans)
    if regex:
        Trans.append(regex)
    else:
        Trans.append(np.nan)


for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    price= i.find('div',class_="_18ToE").text
    yoo = price.split("₹")[1].replace(",","")
    Price.append(yoo)

Year=[]
car_name=[]
Add = []
Kmt=[]
fuel=[]
Trans=[]
Price = []
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= r"\b\d{4}\b"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        Year.append(regex[0])
    else:
        Year.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= " \w+"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        car_name.append(regex)
    else:
        car_name.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    add = i.find('span',class_="_3DYbK")
    if add:
        Add.append(add.text)
    else:
        Add.append(np.nan)
Kmt=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"\d{1,3},\d{2,3}|[,]\d{1,3}"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        Kmt.append(regex)
    else:
        Kmt.append(np.nan)

fuel=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"Petrol|Diesel"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        fuel.append(regex)
    else:
        fuel.append(np.nan)



for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    trans = i.find('ul',class_='_1hOnS').text
    pattern= r"Manual|Automatic"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,trans)
    if regex:
        Trans.append(regex)
    else:
        Trans.append(np.nan)


for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    price= i.find('div',class_="_18ToE").text
    yoo = price.split("₹")[1].replace(",","")
    Price.append(yoo)
    
    
print(Year)

print(fuel)
print(Trans)
print(Price)

Year=[]
car_name=[]
Add = []
Kmt=[]
fuel=[]
Trans=[]
Price = []
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= r"\b\d{4}\b"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        Year.append(regex[0])
    else:
        Year.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= " \w+"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        car_name.append(regex)
    else:
        car_name.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    add = i.find('span',class_="_3DYbK")
    if add:
        Add.append(add.text)
    else:
        Add.append(np.nan)
Kmt=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"\d{1,3},\d{2,3}|[,]\d{1,3}"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        Kmt.append(regex)
    else:
        Kmt.append(np.nan)

fuel=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"Petrol|Diesel"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        fuel.append(regex)
    else:
        fuel.append(np.nan)



for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    trans = i.find('ul',class_='_1hOnS').text
    pattern= r"Manual|Automatic"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,trans)
    if regex:
        Trans.append(regex)
    else:
        Trans.append(np.nan)


for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    price= i.find('div',class_="_18ToE").text
    yoo = price.split("₹")[1].replace(",","")
    Price.append(yoo)

Year=[]
car_name=[]
Add = []
Kmt=[]
fuel=[]
Trans=[]
Price = []
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= r"\b\d{4}\b"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        Year.append(regex[0])
    else:
        Year.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= " \w+"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        car_name.append(regex)
    else:
        car_name.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    add = i.find('span',class_="_3DYbK")
    if add:
        Add.append(add.text)
    else:
        Add.append(np.nan)
Kmt=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"\d{1,3},\d{2,3}|[,]\d{1,3}"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        Kmt.append(regex)
    else:
        Kmt.append(np.nan)

fuel=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"Petrol|Diesel"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        fuel.append(regex)
    else:
        fuel.append(np.nan)



for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    trans = i.find('ul',class_='_1hOnS').text
    pattern= r"Manual|Automatic"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,trans)
    if regex:
        Trans.append(regex)
    else:
        Trans.append(np.nan)


for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    price= i.find('div',class_="_18ToE").text
    yoo = price.split("₹")[1].replace(",","")
    Price.append(yoo)

Year=[]
car_name=[]
Add = []
Kmt=[]
fuel=[]
Trans=[]
Price = []
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= r"\b\d{4}\b"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        Year.append(regex[0])
    else:
        Year.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= " \w+"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        car_name.append(regex)
    else:
        car_name.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    add = i.find('span',class_="_3DYbK")
    if add:
        Add.append(add.text)
    else:
        Add.append(np.nan)
Kmt=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"\d{1,3},\d{2,3}|[,]\d{1,3}"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        Kmt.append(regex)
    else:
        Kmt.append(np.nan)

fuel=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"Petrol|Diesel"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        fuel.append(regex)
    else:
        fuel.append(np.nan)



for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    trans = i.find('ul',class_='_1hOnS').text
    pattern= r"Manual|Automatic"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,trans)
    if regex:
        Trans.append(regex)
    else:
        Trans.append(np.nan)


for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    price= i.find('div',class_="_18ToE").text
    yoo = price.split("₹")[1].replace(",","")
    Price.append(yoo)

Year=[]
car_name=[]
Add = []
Kmt=[]
fuel=[]
Trans=[]
Price = []
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= r"\b\d{4}\b"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        Year.append(regex[0])
    else:
        Year.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    year = i.find('h3',class_='_2lmIw').text
    pattern= " \w+"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,year)
    if regex:
        car_name.append(regex)
    else:
        car_name.append(np.nan)

for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    add = i.find('span',class_="_3DYbK")
    if add:
        Add.append(add.text)
    else:
        Add.append(np.nan)
Kmt=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"\d{1,3},\d{2,3}|[,]\d{1,3}"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        Kmt.append(regex)
    else:
        Kmt.append(np.nan)

fuel=[]
for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    kmt = i.find('ul',class_='_13yb6').text
    pattern= r"Petrol|Diesel"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,kmt)
    if regex:
        fuel.append(regex)
    else:
        fuel.append(np.nan)



for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    trans = i.find('ul',class_='_1hOnS').text
    pattern= r"Manual|Automatic"
    regex= re.findall(pattern,trans)
    if regex:
        Trans.append(regex)
    else:
        Trans.append(np.nan)


for i in soup.find_all('div',class_="_2z-Yu"):
    price= i.find('div',class_="_18ToE").text
    yoo = price.split("₹")[1].replace(",","")
    Price.append(yoo)

Handling with structural errors¶

In [198]:
#For removing []for transmission colum
df['Transmission'] = df['Transmission'].apply(lambda x: x[0])

#For removing [] for fuel type column
def clean_fuel_type(fuel_list):
    if isinstance(fuel_list, list):
        return fuel_list[0]
    else:
        return fuel_list
df['Fuel type'] = df['Fuel type'].apply(clean_fuel_type)

#For creating one more column by extracting 
df['Brand']=[i[0] for i in df['Name of Cars']]

#For removing [] from them
df['Name Of Cars'] = [" ".join(i[0::]) for i in df['Name of Cars']]

#For new column order
new_order = ['Name Of Cars', 'Brand', 'Registration Year','Transmission','Fuel type','Kmt run','Price','Location of car','Name of Cars']
df = df.reindex(columns=new_order)

#For dropping column
df.drop('Name of Cars',axis=1,inplace=True)

#for removing \n from location column
df['Location of car'] = df['Location of car'].replace('.\n','',regex=True)


#to convert nan=np.nan
df["Kmt run"] = df["Kmt run"].replace("nan",np.nan)

df['City Name'] = [i.split(",")[-1] for i in df['Location of car']]

    if ',' in i:
        new.append(i.split(",")[0])
    else:
        new.append(i)
